quran[11{c,v,t}:
21,102,is ki sarsarahat taq nah sُnin ge aur woh hamesha hamesha apni mann bhaatii cheezon ke darmain rahen ge
21,103,"woh intahi ghabrahat ka waqt unn ko zara pareshan nah kere ga, aur mulaika barh kar unn ko hathon haath len ge ke"" yeh tumhara wohi din hai jis ka tum se wada kya jata tha """
21,104,"woh din jabkay aasman ko hum yun lapait kar rakh den ge jaisay tomaar mein ourak lapait diye jatay hain jis terhan pehlay hum ne takhleeq ki ibtida ki thi usi terhan hum phir uss ka iada karen ge yeh aik wada hai hamaray zimmay, aur yeh kaam hamein behar haal karna hai"
21,105,aur zaboor mein hum nasiyaat ke baad yeh likh chuke hain ke zameen ke waris hamaray naik bande hon ge
21,106,iss mein aik barri khabar hai ibadat guzaar logon ke liye
21,107,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne jo tum ko bheja hai to yeh darasal duniya walon ke haq mein hamari rehmat hai"
21,108,"inn se kaho"" mere paas jo wahi aati hai woh yeh hai ke tumhara khuda sirf aik khuda hai, phir kya tum sar-e itaat jhukate ho? """
21,109,"agar woh mun phairen to keh do ke"" mein ne Ali al-elaan tum ko khabardaar kar diya hai ab yeh mein nahi jaanta ke woh cheez jis ka tum se wada kya ja raha hai qareeb hai ya door"
21,110,Allah woh baatein bhi jaanta hai jo ba aawaz buland kahi jati hain aur woh bhi jo tum chhupa kar karte ho
21,111,"mein to yeh samjhta hon ke shayad yeh ( der ) tumahray liye aik fitnah hai aur tumhe aik waqt khaas taq ke liye mazay karne ka mauqa diya ja raha hai """
21,112,"( aakhir kaar ) Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne kaha ke"" ae mere rab, haq ke sath faisla kar day, aur logo, tum jo baatein banatay ho unn ke muqablay mein hamara Rab Rehman hi hamaray liye madad ka sahara hai """
